# Recurring event dialogue (outside the intro sequence).
# Format: see data/dialogue/school.dlg.

# Uncle's biweekly rent collection. Played in the morning of every second
# week. The $2000 charge is applied by Main when this dialogue ends.
[uncle_rent]
Uncle: Morning. You know what day it is.
You: ...Rent.
Uncle: Rent. Two grand. Roof, heat, power - none of it's free, and it's been two weeks.
You: I know, I know.
Uncle: Then hand it over. I'd rather not have the spreadsheet conversation again.
You: Here. Two thousand.
Uncle: Good. See? Painless. Do it on time and we stay friends.
Uncle: Now go on. Whatever you're up to down there, keep it quiet.

# Robot's morning suspicion after a badly-scored night. Only reachable once the
# player has animated part of the robot AND scored 20% or less overnight.
[robot_suspicious]
Her: ...You're back.
Her: Last night felt... wrong. Uneven. Like something kept slipping.
You: It was a rough test. That's all.
Her: No. It was more than rough.
Her: The power kept surging, the panels kept working loose... Did something happen out there?
You: ...Why do you ask?
Her: Because it felt like someone almost found us.
Her: If something suspicious happened last night, I'd rather you told me.
Thoughts: She's more aware than I thought...
You: ...It was nothing. Get some rest.

# Patrol-drone random inspection after a school/work session where the player
# did NOT steal. Routine, no consequences.
[drone_clean]
A patrol drone drops out of the dark and hovers at eye level. A pale scanning beam sweeps you head to toe.
Drone: HOLD. RANDOM COMPLIANCE INSPECTION IN PROGRESS.
You freeze and keep your hands where it can see them.
Drone: SCAN COMPLETE. NO CONTRABAND DETECTED. NO OUTSTANDING FLAGS.
Drone: CITIZEN COMPLIANCE: SATISFACTORY. RESUME YOUR EVENING.
The drone pivots and drifts back into the dark as fast as it came.
Thoughts: ...That was close enough.

# Patrol-drone random inspection after a session where the player DID steal.
# Documents the crime: permanent +5 suspicion floor plus +20 suspicion overall,
# applied by Main when this dialogue ends.
[drone_caught]
A patrol drone drops out of the dark and hovers at eye level. A pale scanning beam sweeps you head to toe.
Drone: HOLD. RANDOM COMPLIANCE INSPECTION IN PROGRESS.
The beam stops on your bag. It turns red.
Drone: CONTRABAND DETECTED. UNAUTHORIZED ACQUISITION LOGGED AGAINST YOUR CITIZEN RECORD.
Drone: THIS INFRACTION HAS BEEN DOCUMENTED WITH THE DEPARTMENT OF CIVIL COMPLIANCE, DIVISION OF BEHAVIORAL OVERSIGHT.
Drone: YOU ARE NOW DESIGNATED A PERSON OF INTEREST. YOUR MOVEMENTS WILL BE MONITORED WITH INCREASED FREQUENCY.
Drone: A FLAGGED RECORD CANNOT BE CLEARED. IT CAN ONLY BE MANAGED. DO NOT REOFFEND.
The drone holds its red light on you a moment longer, then withdraws into the dark.
Thoughts: They'll be watching me closely now. That part doesn't wash off.
